Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.56,0:00:24.14,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃烧吧 沉睡心底的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.23,0:00:30.19,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奔跑吧 向充满希望的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.94,0:00:33.28,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,40)}无论倒下多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.74,0:00:36.11,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都要再次站立起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.66,0:00:42.00,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是等待 奇迹岂会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.45,0:00:46.79,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越吧 昨日懦弱的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.04,0:00:52.80,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧握住 浮于银河的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.97,0:00:54.88,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,40)}不要屈服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.22,0:00:57.84,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驰骋的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.01,0:00:59.30,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,40)}向着梦想之地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.39,0:01:01.56,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇往直前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.81,0:01:07.02,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘着这天马的羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.48,0:01:12.86,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣斗士星矢 炽热燃烧的真心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.36,0:01:18.49,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信决不屈服的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.91,0:01:26.42,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣斗士星矢 决不停滞决不放弃的勇者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.75,0:01:33.76,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(40,0)}直指Ω　奋勇战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.06,0:00:19.33,LOGO,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光荣&galaxy字幕组
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.26,0:00:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当世间面临邪恶之神的侵略时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.37,0:00:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便必定会出现奋起迎战的战士 圣斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.05,0:00:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻 年轻圣斗士们崭新的传说即将展开
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.13,0:01:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙等人在第六宫处女宫成功会合
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.02,0:01:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 守护处女宫的处女座Virgo的不动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.67,0:01:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有着在黄金圣斗士中也数一数二的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.68,0:01:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正当年轻的圣斗士们耗尽力量之时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.25,0:02:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛尔斯的儿子伊甸出现在了他们面前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.63,0:02:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距地球被黑暗所笼罩还有7小时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.84,0:02:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…头发的颜色…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.70,0:02:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸 为何至此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是为一战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.51,0:02:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是收拾青铜圣斗士的话 吾一人足矣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.51,0:02:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们根本无法使我移动分毫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.14,0:03:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 所以我才来此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.00,0:03:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就为与你一战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇敢的反叛！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.80,0:03:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸 决心的斗志！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.93,0:03:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是反叛者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.79,0:03:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些人要打倒玛尔斯 而你要与他们同流合污吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.92,0:03:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我只为通过此处而战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是玛尔斯之子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.22,0:03:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是应该可以在这十二宫中自由走动的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.64,0:03:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在已经不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.61,0:03:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为对父亲来说 我已经成为了叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.75,0:03:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲的理想十分崇高 但实现方式却是错误的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我决心要让父亲清醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.89,0:03:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此 在守护父亲的圣斗士中 被誉为拥有最强小宇宙的你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.73,0:04:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我必须要打倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.45,0:04:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好强的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比以前又倍增了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.83,0:04:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不错的小宇宙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.47,0:04:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 玛尔斯之子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.83,0:04:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是想要阻碍这个世界的净化
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.62,0:04:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是你 也不可以迈过这处女宫半步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明王来临
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.17,0:05:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.73,0:05:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不动的攻击被破解了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.64,0:05:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷光火星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.06,0:05:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 竟轻易破解了我的五大明王
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.95,0:05:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就轮到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.85,0:05:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的攻击对我完全不疼不痒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.48,0:05:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种程度的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.42,0:05:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本无法令我移动分毫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.81,0:06:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,识相些 速速退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.16,0:06:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要通过这里 前往父亲那里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.58,0:06:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸的攻击奏效了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.86,0:06:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸行断罪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.83,0:06:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是玛尔斯的继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.33,0:06:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可因一时冲动而莽撞行事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.38,0:06:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂且冷静一下头脑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.09,0:06:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.08,0:06:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要助伊甸一臂之力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:06:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷电龙卷风
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.42,0:07:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽只有一瞬间…但你竟能令我移动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.25,0:07:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来并非仅仅出于对父亲的憎恨与愤怒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.54,0:07:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尚有其他的原因 驱使你前进呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.24,0:07:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟所为何事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悔恨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是悔恨 不动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悔恨？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.52,0:07:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西亦能化作力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.87,0:07:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.69,0:07:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确 一直以来认为自己是绝对正确 引导着世界走入正轨的你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.20,0:07:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不可能理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.85,0:07:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 看来为了回应你的决心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.75,0:07:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也应前往更高的层次才是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更高的层次？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.61,0:07:58.75,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指自性轮身、正法轮身、教令轮身三者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.61,0:07:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身具三身 称为三轮身
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.09,0:08:04.26,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教令輪身（きょうりょうりんしん）：大日如来为教化刚强难度的众生，现大忿怒相以降伏之。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.09,0:08:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一为借暴力阻止忤逆者的恐怖之身
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.84,0:08:08.66,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正法輪身（しょうぼうりんしん）：大日如来垂迹现菩萨身，以正法化益众生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.84,0:08:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一为静静教诲宇宙真理之身
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.35,0:08:14.54,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自性輪身（じしょうりんしん）：曼荼罗中台大日如来以本地自性的佛体化益众生， 因此称为自性轮身。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.35,0:08:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一身乃 化自身为顿悟之身
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.00,0:08:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.57,0:08:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已无需战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.13,0:08:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉浸于我的世界中 平静地离去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.61,0:09:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好柔和的风
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.53,0:09:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水声潺潺入耳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.16,0:09:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森林的香气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中的烈焰好像渐渐平息了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.55,0:09:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离去…那种事我可做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.28,0:09:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不动 我会继续战斗 直到你让路为止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.59,0:09:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实乃一众可怜之人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼见如此纯洁清澈之世 仍执意言战
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.33,0:09:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的内心不会平静
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.92,0:09:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直至完成阿莉雅的愿望之前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.11,0:09:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不动 你不会明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了愿意倾尽生命守护之人的世界 是什么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.70,0:09:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔？那是怎样的世界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.96,0:09:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是绝望的世界 痛失光芒的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.31,0:10:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明可以阻止玛尔斯的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.45,0:10:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你却只是眼睁睁地看着 什么也没做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 想让你老爹醒悟也为时已晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错 太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.59,0:10:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诚如所言 我什么也做不到 什么也没去做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.30,0:10:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今唯有这份悔恨在激励我前进
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无意与你们并肩作战
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 少碍事！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.49,0:10:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那群人是很碍事的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.47,0:10:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且即使他们离开这里 无法打败我的人亦无法前行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.37,0:11:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾便于此 为汝忤逆亲父之罪行 施予断罪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.42,0:11:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛尔斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.94,0:11:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸只是为一时感情困扰而陷入迷乱 您不必担心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.55,0:11:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛尔斯大人的伟志 自他幼时起我便令其耳濡目染
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.03,0:11:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他应当已经充分理解了自身的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.18,0:11:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先行失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.88,0:11:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙 光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸呢 不管他了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.39,0:12:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙不想和我们并肩战斗 还把我们赶出了处女宫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.69,0:12:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的目的是打倒玛尔斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之就把不动交给伊甸 继续前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.22,0:12:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 伊甸救了我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙一定不会有事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.44,0:12:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那家伙毕竟是玛尔斯的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.26,0:12:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青铜圣斗士们突破了处女宫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.64,0:12:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青铜圣斗士？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距玛尔斯大人夙愿得偿仅一步之遥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.67,0:12:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是时候送那些碍事之人回老家了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.80,0:12:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就穿起这件圣衣 将他们送向时间的尽头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.03,0:13:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 这就是你所渴求的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.04,0:13:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄金圣斗士？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开自己的宫殿了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.63,0:13:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得那家伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.46,0:13:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荣斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙本应该是时钟座的白银圣斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.21,0:13:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是执掌时间与永恒的水瓶座
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.89,0:13:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarius的黄金圣斗士 时贞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.15,0:13:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀害大哥的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.79,0:13:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为黄金圣斗士了么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你有印象
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,0:13:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里邂逅过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是无论是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.08,0:13:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都不会再向上一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.13,0:13:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是谁阻拦 我们都要去上面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.46,0:14:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然脸和以前一样 但总觉得哪里不对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.47,0:14:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉有些不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.80,0:14:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他们收拾了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.19,0:14:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间拳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.90,0:14:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.21,0:14:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.71,0:14:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙刚一消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.49,0:14:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个瞬间就被揍了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.39,0:14:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的速度已经快到肉眼无法看到的程度了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.40,0:14:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗 战斗吧 时贞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.51,0:14:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他们收拾了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.29,0:14:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气息在流动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.41,0:14:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么移动得那么慢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.29,0:14:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间拳 3秒后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.79,0:14:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.01,0:15:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那家伙的速度快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是我们变慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.15,0:15:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间的流动发生了变化
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.64,0:15:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 可以操纵时间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.69,0:15:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以做到那种事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就用比时间还快的光速来击中他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.38,0:15:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马流星拳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.91,0:15:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.52,0:15:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你攻击到我需要8秒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.56,0:15:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.81,0:15:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4秒后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.87,0:15:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3 2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.38,0:15:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 轮到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.74,0:15:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此游刃有余的狙击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来 简直没法战斗了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.04,0:15:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这股力量太异常了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.45,0:15:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就像被圣衣上浮现出的那骷髅命令似的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.37,0:16:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生物皆为时间之奴仆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对生物来说 最难对付的对手就是时间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.76,0:16:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说 自我获得这件圣衣时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.65,0:16:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我便是最强的圣斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.81,0:16:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡是圣斗士 无人不希望自己能身披这水瓶座黃金圣衣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.03,0:16:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你穿也可以喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.98,0:16:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿上这件圣衣 你就能最大限度地发挥力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.02,0:16:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也包括驾驭时间的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.81,0:16:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 有个条件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.87,0:16:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,条件？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为这件圣衣的奴仆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.37,0:16:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奴仆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.62,0:16:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件圣衣有强烈的自我意识
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.79,0:16:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在被圣衣的自我承认之前 你要做它的奴仆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.93,0:17:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 只要能够获得驾驭时间的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始你就是水瓶座的黄金圣斗士了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.79,0:17:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵守圣衣的命令吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.88,0:17:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现在开始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.42,0:17:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是水瓶座的黄金圣斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.82,0:17:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将对这件圣衣言听计从
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.31,0:17:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们怎么能被打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.08,0:17:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里放弃的话就没有未来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.91,0:17:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.90,0:17:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间在继续流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.79,0:17:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你们几个的时间就到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.68,0:17:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不会到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.25,0:17:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.37,0:18:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此处乃审判之间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.86,0:18:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.20,0:18:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体不听使唤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.58,0:18:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.68,0:18:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝身为玛尔斯之子 前途似锦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.83,0:18:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何却要忤逆亲父
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.22,0:18:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.06,0:18:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到父亲身边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.76,0:18:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭借自己的双脚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.86,0:18:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭借自己的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.85,0:18:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.92,0:18:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来唇舌之力已不能令你动摇了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.49,0:18:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菩提证悟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.46,0:19:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还打算战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.05,0:19:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宇宙在燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.62,0:19:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年们在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.10,0:19:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到自己应做之事 相信它
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.22,0:19:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并一心一意勇往直前的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.39,0:19:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 少年们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.56,0:19:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给他们致命一击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.27,0:19:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.78,0:19:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.77,0:19:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.49,0:20:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.53,0:20:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍有站起来的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你力量的源泉究竟是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.96,0:20:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是祈愿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.29,0:20:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她所祈愿的世界的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.04,0:20:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个祈愿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.43,0:20:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我力量的源泉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.60,0:20:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.28,0:20:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他觉醒了第七感吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.41,0:21:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.68,0:21:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.18,0:21:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝曾言要让玛尔斯醒悟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.90,0:21:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便醒悟 又有何用？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.28,0:21:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创造一个没有战争且美丽平静的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.23,0:21:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲想用力量重置这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.09,0:21:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不同
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.31,0:21:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美丽的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.82,0:21:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不应该建立在现存的生命的牺牲之上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.52,0:21:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美丽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.15,0:21:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻的心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.50,0:21:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菩提证悟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.41,0:21:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这招来结束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.39,0:21:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猎户恸灭（Orion's Devastation)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.52,0:22:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙一行人再次见到了天秤座玄武
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.23,0:22:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善恶分明的天秤座圣斗士玄武
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.31,0:22:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的行动和之前黄金圣斗士大相径庭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.78,0:22:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时贞与玄武
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.48,0:22:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最高阶圣斗士间的禁忌之战即将拉开帷幕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.12,0:22:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 圣斗士星矢Ω
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.95,0:22:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天秤宫的再会！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.48,0:22:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激突、黄金对黄金！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.98,0:22:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾感受到小宇宙的存在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
